WHAT CHANGED (window root background refactor)
- Restored the full-window liquid-glass layer and made the window non-opaque so glass samples behind the window.
- The window can still render a user-provided background image behind all UI when `WINDOW_BACKGROUND_IMAGE_PATH` is set.
- Introduced a single base glass-style source (`baseGlassStyleTintColor()`) so components that previously referenced
